OL,3,CStarmer facing crunch day as Cabinet
OL,4,Cministers tell him to consider position
OL,6,FThe rebellion against Sir Keir
OL,7,FStarmer's leadership is now growing,
OL,8,Fas GMB's Louisa James reports from
OL,9,Foutside No 10
OL,11,FKeir Starmer is facing the biggest
OL,12,Fchallenge to his leadership yet after
OL,13,Fnumerous Cabinet members called on him
OL,14,Fto consider his position following
OL,15,Flast week's disastrous local election
OL,16,Fresults.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
