OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778569553
OL,3,CStarmer facing crunch day as Cabinet
OL,4,Cministers tell him to consider position
OL,6,FITV News understands four ministers,
OL,7,Fled by the home secretary, went into
OL,8,FNumber 10 on Monday evening and told
OL,9,Fhim to consider setting out a
OL,10,Ftimetable to resign.
OL,12,FForeign Secretary Yvette Cooper is
OL,13,Freported to have been alongside
OL,14,FShabana Mahmood, meaning two of
OL,15,FStarmer's most senior government
OL,16,Fmembers were at the meeting.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
