CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778569553
OL,3,CStarmer facing crunch day as Cabinet
OL,4,Cministers tell him to consider position
OL,6,FStarmer also suffered several
OL,7,Fresignations from ministerial aides on
OL,8,FMonday. They joined dozens of
OL,9,Fbackbench Labour MPs calling for him
OL,10,Fto quit.
OL,12,FThe resignations came just hours after
OL,13,Fthe PM made a speech designed to
OL,14,Freboot his government, promising
OL,15,Fsweeping changes to unite his party
OL,16,Fand the country.
OL,18,FThe PM has so far resisted all calls
OL,19,Fto resign and quickly appointed
OL,20,Freplacements for all of the aides who
OL,21,Fquit.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778569553
OL,3,CStarmer facing crunch day as Cabinet
OL,4,Cministers tell him to consider position
OL,6,FThe Cabinet is due to meet on Tuesday
OL,7,Fmorning at 9.30.
OL,9,FITV News has spoken to and tracked
OL,10,Fonline 78 MPs who think the prime
OL,11,Fminister should immediately set out a
OL,12,Ftimeline for his departure - and a
OL,13,Ffurther eight who believe he should
OL,14,Fleave if things do not improve.
OL,16,FLabour lost almost 1,500 English
OL,17,Fcouncillors in last week's local
OL,18,Felections, faced a near wipe-out in
OL,19,FWales and went backwards in Scotland.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778569553
OL,3,CStarmer facing crunch day as Cabinet
OL,4,Cministers tell him to consider position
OL,6,FSeats were lost all over the country
OL,7,Fto Reform and the Greens, with
OL,8,Fdramatic results such as in Wakefield,
OL,9,Fwhere Labour lost 56 seats, and Reform
OL,10,Fgained 58.
OL,12,FStarmer's speech did prompt former
OL,13,Fminister Catherine West to withdraw
OL,14,Fher imminent threat to launch a
OL,15,Fleadership challenge, which she issued
OL,16,Fin the days after the election results.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
