PN,30206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778569553
OL,3,CStarmer facing crunch day as Cabinet
OL,4,Cministers tell him to consider position
OL,6,FWest had previously said she would
OL,7,Fchallenge Starmer for the party
OL,8,Fleadership as early as Monday
OL,9,Fafternoon, but has now said he should
OL,10,Fquit by September.
OL,12,FA handful of backbenchers have spoken
OL,13,Fin support of the prime minister, with
OL,14,FMacclesfield MP Tim Roca and Gedling's
OL,15,FMichael Payne saying Starmer had
OL,16,Fdemonstrated he understood "the scale
OL,17,Fof the challenge" facing the country.
